name: Studds Chrome Elite Black 580 Mm Helmet
descriptions:
• Brand:STUDDS
  • Model:Chrome Elite
  • Product Code:SCE_BLK
  • Chrome Elite is a full face helmet with product features like regulated density EPS, hypoallergenic liner, quick release visor and quick release chin strap. Chrome Elite comes in various sizes and colour options
  • Convenience to the rider for changing visors when required
  • Protects rider from allergies or infections arising from continuous contact with damp helmet liners due to extended riding or on hot/rainy days
  • The outer shell is injected with special high impact grade of engineering thermoplastic for extra protection
  • Ease of operation for the rider or during any unfortunate impact
  • Country of Origin: ?India.
